---
title: Creamy Peanut Ramen
---

Cook @instant ramen{2%packs} according to package directions. Reserve 1/2 cup of the cooking water, then drain noodles and set aside.

In a bowl, whisk together the seasoning packets from the ramen, @eggs{2}, @kewpie mayo{2%tbsp}, @peanut butter{2%tbsp}, @garlic cloves{3} (minced), @spring onion{} (chopped), and @sesame oil{1%tsp}. Thin with the reserved @cooking water{1/2%cup} and mix until smooth.

Toss cooked noodles with the peanut sauce. Garnish with extra spring onion, @chili oil{}, and @sesame seeds{}.
